snippet.title: Don Duality - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Don Duality is a tycoon game with card mechanics. Send your gangsters to beat out debts, rob banks, steal valuables and launder the money they earn in your establishment. Hire staff for your restaurant and upgrade it, but be careful! Not many people can sit on two chairs at once.

Follow us on social media to stay up to date on the latest news:

https://twitter.com/don_duality
https://www.reddit.com/r/DonDuality
